<ab facs="#facs_111_r1l22">bürg ſeyt . Tun wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> ʒu wıſſen . daʒ vns dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıe </ab>
