<ab facs="#facs_111_r1l24"><expan>frawnberg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ſchulde bıſ her <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒogen</expan> vnd niht becʒalt hat . <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_111_r1l25">ſo <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt fleıſſ Jr wellt ſchıken vnd <expan>beſtell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_111_r1l26">wır <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſchulde noch <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒogenlıch</expan> becʒalt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
